        <mxCell id="upgrade-engine-desc" value="• Detect framework + versions&#xa;• Select applicable rules (40 total)&#xa;• Scan target repo (regex patterns)&#xa;• Assess impact: occurrences, effort&#xa;• 4 frameworks: Angular, Spring,&#xa;  Java, Playwright&#xa;• Conditional: only task_type=&quot;upgrade&quot;" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=9;" vertex="1" parent="1">
